{"id":"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http","title":"Understanding communicating with backend services using HTTP","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/understanding-communicating-with-http.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\" translation-result=\"on\">了解使用 HTTP 与后端服务通信<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Understanding communicating with backend services using HTTP<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">大多数前端应用都要通过 HTTP 协议与服务器通讯，才能下载或上传数据并访问其它后端服务。Angular 给应用提供了一个 HTTP 客户端 API，也就是 <code>@angular/common/<a href=\"api/common/http\" class=\"code-anchor\">http</a></code> 中的 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 服务类。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Most front-end applications need to communicate with a server over the HTTP protocol, to download or upload data and access other back-end services. Angular provides a client HTTP API for Angular applications, the <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> service class in <code>@angular/common/<a href=\"api/common/http\" class=\"code-anchor\">http</a></code>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClientModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClientModule</a></code> 之前，你应该对下列内容有基本的了解：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Before working with the <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClientModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClientModule</a></code>, you should have a basic understanding of the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">TypeScript 编程</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">TypeScript programming</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">HTTP 协议的用法</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Usage of the HTTP protocol</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 的应用设计基础，就像<a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular 基本概念</a>中描述的那样</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular application-design fundamentals, as described in <a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular Concepts</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Observable 的技术和运算符。请参阅 <a href=\"guide/observables\">Observables 指南</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Observable techniques and operators.\nSee the <a href=\"guide/observables\">Observables guide</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"http-client-service-features\" translation-result=\"on\">HTTP 客户端服务特性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#http-client-service-features\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">HTTP client service features<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#http-client-service-features\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">HTTP 客户端服务提供了以下主要功能。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The HTTP client service offers the following major features.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">请求<a href=\"guide/http-request-data-from-server\">类型化响应对象</a>的能力</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The ability to request <a href=\"guide/http-request-data-from-server\">typed response objects</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">管道式<a href=\"guide/http-handle-request-errors\">错误处理</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Streamlined <a href=\"guide/http-handle-request-errors\">error handling</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/http-test-requests\">可测试性</a>的特性</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/http-test-requests\">Testability</a> features</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">对请求和响应的<a href=\"guide/http-intercept-requests-and-responses\">拦截</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Request and response <a href=\"guide/http-intercept-requests-and-responses\">interception</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What's next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/http-server-communication\">建立服务器通信</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/http-server-communication\">Setup for server communication</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：3/14/2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/http\n - api/common/http/HttpClient\n - api/common/http/HttpClientModule\n - guide/architecture\n - guide/http-handle-request-errors\n - guide/http-intercept-requests-and-responses\n - guide/http-request-data-from-server\n - guide/http-server-communication\n - guide/http-test-requests\n - guide/observables\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#http-client-service-features\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#http-客户端服务特性\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#prerequisites\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#understanding-communicating-with-backend-services-using-http\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#whats-next\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#下一步呢\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#了解使用-http-与后端服务通信\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http#前提条件\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/understanding-communicating-with-http.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"}